How to set up dotfiles

1) alias dotfiles="/usr/bin/git --git-dir=$HOME/.dotfiles --work-tree=$HOME"
2) git clone --bare git@github.com:svenjacobs/dotfiles.git $HOME/.dotfiles
3) dotfiles checkout
4) dotfiles config --local status.showUntrackedFiles no

Also read https://www.atlassian.com/git/tutorials/dotfiles

